   1:FFT.h         **** /*
   2:FFT.h         ****  * Simple iterative radix-2 FFT class (float)
   3:FFT.h         ****  * - Precomputes twiddle factors for the current FFT size
   4:FFT.h         ****  * - In-place complex FFT (real[] and imag[] arrays provided by caller)
   5:FFT.h         ****  * - Simple real-FFT wrapper: runs complex FFT on real input (imag zeros) and returns full complex 
   6:FFT.h         ****  *
   7:FFT.h         ****  * Usage:
   8:FFT.h         ****  *   FFT fft;
